<p t="46530" d="5339" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​It&#39;s two days after​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​Suzune-san hit the transfer student.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="51869" d="4504" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​It seems she&#39;s come to apologize for that...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="56373" d="2903" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Heh... Hi...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="59276" d="1135" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="60411" d="3703" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​So, like, how ya been? Haha...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="64548" d="1735" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​S-Suzune-san?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="66483" d="3804" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​You too, Touka-san.​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="6">​ ​What&#39;s the matter?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="70287" d="4304" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​Suzune-san, it would be best​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="5">​ ​if you came right out with it.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="74591" d="2570" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​I-I know...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="77494" d="1902" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​Um... What&#39;s this about?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="79396" d="5773" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​R... Remember when I smacked you​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​the other day?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="85636" d="1635" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​Huh?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="87571" d="2202" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​Oh! That was no big deal at all!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="89773" d="1669" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​I-I&#39;m sorry!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="91442" d="4004" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​I got carried away and​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​hit you harder than I meant to!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="95579" d="3871" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​It&#39;s fine, really!​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="6">​ ​I&#39;d already forgotten about it!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="99450" d="2402" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​If I may elaborate,​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="101852" d="4471" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​Suzune-san has always​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="5">​ ​rather lacked finesse...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="106323" d="2870" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​She really meant no harm.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="109526" d="2169" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​Honestly, I didn&#39;t mind at all!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="112162" d="1535" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​I mean,​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="113864" d="4338" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​Suzune-san just meant it​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="6">​ ​as some friendly bonding, right?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="118202" d="2135" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​E-Exactly!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="120337" d="2169" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​In that case, will you...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="122506" d="5839" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​forgive Suzune-san for what she did?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="128345" d="4204" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Will you... forgive me?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="133050" d="1501" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​Of course!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="134551" d="2836" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Th-Thank goodness!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="137387" d="4271" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​See? All you had to do​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="5">​ ​was explain yourself clearly.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="141658" d="3704" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​But what Inari said got to me...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="145729" d="2136" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​What she said?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="147998" d="3871" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​You mean that rumor​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="6">​ ​about transfer students?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="151869" d="2035" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Y-Yes, that!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="153904" d="3637" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​See, I&#39;d never heard it before.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="157541" d="5138" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​Don&#39;t you worry. I, for one,​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="5">​ ​knew about the rumor,​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="162679" d="2136" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​but I don&#39;t believe it one bit.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="169586" d="1502" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​Huh...?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="171088" d="2669" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Hm? What&#39;s wrong?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="174057" d="2203" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​Th-The classroom looked all weird...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="176593" d="2169" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​And there was this girl...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="179229" d="1535" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​Wh-What&#39;s happening?!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="180764" d="3837" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="7">​ ​I-It&#39;s an earthquake!​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="7">​ ​Everyone take shelter under the desks!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="184601" d="3103" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="8">​ ​I-Inari! It&#39;s okay, we&#39;ll be fine!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="187704" d="4872" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="9">​ ​I-It&#39;s all because we mistreated​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="9">​ ​the transfer student!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="192576" d="2169" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="9">​ ​Help, Hanabi-chan!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="194745" d="2302" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="8">​ ​Just calm down! Please!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="197281" d="834" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="9">​ ​Ahh!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="198115" d="1501" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="8">​ ​I-Inari!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="199917" d="1701" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​I-Inari-san! Hanabi-san!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="203854" d="1935" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​W-We&#39;ll get through this!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="205789" d="2636" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​I-It&#39;s all my fault! All of it!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="208425" d="3270" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="7">​ ​You two! Get under the desks!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="212963" d="1568" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​I don&#39;t understand...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="214865" d="2669" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​What is happening right now?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="219703" d="3270" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​Everything&#39;s gone quiet.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="222973" d="4972" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​All I hear are​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="10">​ ​ambulance sirens in the distance.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="228111" d="4839" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​I&#39;m still alive. But the others...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="236253" d="3236" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​I-Isn&#39;t this...​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="10">​ ​one of the school&#39;s hallways?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="239723" d="3270" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​But why is it intact?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="243260" d="3236" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​I saw the ceiling collapse,​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="246797" d="2702" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​but there&#39;s not​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="10">​ ​a single piece of rubble...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="249833" d="1668" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​What&#39;s going on?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="251802" d="2702" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​And where is everyone?!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="254905" d="1601" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​Th-That&#39;s the girl...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="256907" d="2102" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​I saw in the classroom...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="259176" d="3336" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​Hey! Who are you?​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="6">​ ​Did I survive?!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="262613" d="4404" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​What happened to Aogami High School?​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="6">​ ​Where is everyone?!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="267417" d="3103" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​Please... tell me!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="272956" d="5906" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="11">​ ​So you... must be the transfer student.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="281265" d="1334" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="11">​ ​Hee-hee.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="4989" d="100" wp="3" ws="2" p="12">​</p>
